{"arkId":"cl010495295","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010495295","modified ":"2025-09-08","title":"Chandelier armori\u00e9 avec Aurore, C\u00e9phale et Adonis","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Chandelier armori\u00e9 avec Aurore, C\u00e9phale et Adonis"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Renaissance (Occident)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1850 - 1900","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1850,"endYear":1900,"imprecision":"","text":"2e moiti\u00e9 du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Robillard, Julien","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"?","dates":[{"date":"10\/01\/1822","place":"Coudun (Oise)","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"Emailleur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Manufacture de S\u00e8vres","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q653307"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RFML.OA.2022.2.7","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"\u00e9mail ; chandelier","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Le chandelier \u00e0 base hexagonale est constitu\u00e9 d\u2019un f\u00fbt pourvu de deux n\u0153uds et d\u2019un disque plat, ainsi que d\u2019un binet. Les figurations en grisaille se concentrent sur les quatre m\u00e9daillons ovales du pied \u2013 Aurore, C\u00e9phale, Adonis et un \u00e9cu armori\u00e9 \u2013 et sur le binet \u2013 deux m\u00e9daillons orn\u00e9s de portraits masculins de profil gauche. Le reste de la surface offre un d\u00e9cor v\u00e9g\u00e9talisan